1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 16=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(Qingqing's Playful Disguise
Startles the Crown Prince)

4
00:01:02,030 --> 00:01:03,900
This young lady
has nothing to do with this.

5
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:05,230
Let her go first.

6
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:07,920
I

7
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:11,430
will naturally return to the palace

8
00:01:12,510 --> 00:01:14,230
and explain everything to Father.

9
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:25,480
(Yeah, right.)

10
00:01:25,610 --> 00:01:27,790
(Your father will only become
more suspicious of you.)

11
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:45,710
That scheming fool.

12
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:48,280
With a note
personally written by yours truly,

13
00:01:48,590 --> 00:01:50,590
this should keep you
confined to your residence.

14
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,920
Did it work, Tower Master?

15
00:01:56,230 --> 00:01:57,070
Of course.

16
00:01:57,640 --> 00:02:01,070
Tell Yuanzhao to come to the workshop
after he's finished over there.

17
00:02:01,350 --> 00:02:01,950
Got it.

18
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:08,710
With all these inventions,
I'll make another fortune.

19
00:02:08,710 --> 00:02:09,360
Yuanhe,

20
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,710
how do you explain this?

21
00:02:11,870 --> 00:02:13,310
My conscience is clear.

22
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:15,840
I had already purchased Wangshi Tower

23
00:02:15,910 --> 00:02:17,240
as my private residence.

24
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:20,960
That woman isn't any suspicious person.

25
00:02:21,630 --> 00:02:23,400
Then why was she hiding?

26
00:02:23,870 --> 00:02:26,310
I don't like others looking at my woman.

27
00:02:27,030 --> 00:02:27,800
Yuanhe,

28
00:02:28,470 --> 00:02:30,430
that's quite a far-fetched excuse.

29
00:02:31,030 --> 00:02:33,280
I never believed
those rumors on the street.

30
00:02:33,910 --> 00:02:34,910
But now,

31
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,840
I'm starting to have my doubts.

32
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,150
Besides,

33
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:42,400
the scent on you

34
00:02:43,870 --> 00:02:45,800
is remarkably similar
to the Tower Master's.

35
00:02:47,390 --> 00:02:48,430
You're asking for death!

36
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,280
What's this?

37
00:02:59,910 --> 00:03:01,150
At the end of the Wei Hour,

38
00:03:01,150 --> 00:03:02,430
Wangshi Tower

39
00:03:02,710 --> 00:03:05,280
is willing to trade all its weapons

40
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:05,680
to help

41
00:03:06,430 --> 00:03:09,870
the Crown Prince
ascend to the highest position?

42
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:13,000
I only ask that
Your Highness spare my life.

43
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:14,800
Father, this...

44
00:03:15,260 --> 00:03:17,110
This is the Tower Master's
actual handwriting.

45
00:03:20,630 --> 00:03:21,470
Bring it here.

46
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,280
Yuanhe,

47
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,630
how do you explain this now?

48
00:03:41,310 --> 00:03:43,870
Someone is clearly trying to frame me.

49
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,630
They deliberately slipped this note

50
00:03:46,870 --> 00:03:49,030
into my robes while no one was looking.

51
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,000
Yuanhe,

52
00:03:50,750 --> 00:03:52,080
what do you mean by that?

53
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,630
Are you saying I framed you?

54
00:03:55,430 --> 00:03:56,030
Father,

55
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:57,470
you saw it yourself.

56
00:03:57,840 --> 00:04:00,080
I didn't even touch his sleeve.

57
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:05,470
Yuanhe has behaved
improperly before the throne.

58
00:04:05,950 --> 00:04:07,860
You're confined
to your residence for one month.

59
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,470
The Inspectorate

60
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:11,600
will also be suspended for one month.

61
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,310
Yes.

62
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,310
Petty tricks.

63
00:04:26,630 --> 00:04:28,040
They only know

64
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:30,040
these underhanded tactics.

65
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,430
(He colluded with the rebels,)

66
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:39,000
(and all he gets
is a month's confinement.)

67
00:04:40,630 --> 00:04:43,310
(Father really does favor him.)

68
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:48,750
Tower Master,

69
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:49,680
I've brought him.

70
00:04:56,690 --> 00:04:58,800
Tower Master, you actually
have so much military equipment.

71
00:04:58,800 --> 00:04:59,480
That's none of your business.

72
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,360
Don't ask questions.

73
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,310
Is that scheming Crown Prince dead yet?

74
00:05:02,310 --> 00:05:04,160
The Tower Master's plan really worked.

75
00:05:04,430 --> 00:05:05,600
For the next month,

76
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:08,040
Yuanhe and the Inspectorate
won't be troubling you anymore.

77
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:11,390
It's a shame about my Wangshi Chronicle,

78
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:14,190
and all the silver
I didn't have time to move.

79
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,690
It breaks my heart
just thinking about it.

80
00:05:19,630 --> 00:05:21,000
You've helped me make a fortune,

81
00:05:21,090 --> 00:05:23,120
yet I've dragged you
into danger time and again.

82
00:05:23,310 --> 00:05:25,510
I truly feel guilty about it.

83
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,040
So,

84
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:27,870
Tower Master,

85
00:05:28,270 --> 00:05:29,480
for our next venture,

86
00:05:29,830 --> 00:05:30,750
I'll provide

87
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,040
all the startup capital.

88
00:05:34,300 --> 00:05:36,040
Here's five hundred thousand taels
in banknotes,

89
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:38,070
and the deed
to a shop in the busy market.

90
00:05:38,270 --> 00:05:42,240
I'd like to do my part
to help launch your next enterprise.

91
00:05:45,430 --> 00:05:47,630
I haven't doted on you for nothing.

92
00:05:51,190 --> 00:05:52,070
Then let's treat this

93
00:05:52,070 --> 00:05:54,040
as your investment in the new venture.

94
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,870
Once we make a profit,

95
00:05:56,490 --> 00:05:57,560
you'll get thirty percent.

96
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:59,430
After listening to you,

97
00:05:59,430 --> 00:06:01,000
I know exactly what to do next.

98
00:06:01,830 --> 00:06:04,240
That scheming fool
thinks he's beaten me.

99
00:06:04,430 --> 00:06:06,870
I'm not going down that easily.

100
00:06:07,830 --> 00:06:09,270
My next target

101
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,310
is a bank.

102
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:13,950
Tower Master,

103
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,800
are you planning to rob a bank?

104
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,120
Good idea.

105
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,800
I mean we're going to open a bank.

106
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:29,800
Charge people to deposit money.

107
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:31,190
Lend money at compound interest.

108
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:33,240
That's not a bank.

109
00:06:33,390 --> 00:06:36,430
It's practically
a money printing machine.

110
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:38,920
Besides, we also have

111
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:40,680
highly skilled trained assassins.

112
00:06:41,330 --> 00:06:43,120
Others worry about
robberies and bad debts.

113
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,270
I don't.

114
00:06:44,830 --> 00:06:45,800
Just to be safe,

115
00:06:46,070 --> 00:06:49,600
you'll be the bank's public manager.

116
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,720
I'll do whatever the Tower Master says.

117
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:53,040
Whatever the Tower Master says, I'll do.

118
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:55,190
You little rascal.

119
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,680
You're impossible not to like.

120
00:06:58,270 --> 00:07:00,120
All right. Blindfold him
and send him back.

121
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:01,360
Yes.

122
00:07:01,390 --> 00:07:02,720
Tower Master, wait.

123
00:07:03,070 --> 00:07:04,000
Throw him out.

124
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,240
You...

125
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:09,240
Right now, our top priority

126
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:11,310
is to make the bank well known.

127
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:13,390
Since we can't use
the Wangshi Chronicle anymore,

128
00:07:15,190 --> 00:07:16,390
we'll use this instead.

129
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:19,870
Jiuzhu.

130
00:07:19,950 --> 00:07:20,600
You

131
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,430
will lead the others and slip these flyers

132
00:07:22,430 --> 00:07:24,870
under every door.

133
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,240
Then use this printing block

134
00:07:26,630 --> 00:07:27,870
to stamp every wall you see

135
00:07:27,890 --> 00:07:29,190
and print every patch
of ground you find.

136
00:07:30,870 --> 00:07:32,240
I'm an assassin.

137
00:07:32,310 --> 00:07:33,950
Think bigger.

138
00:07:34,100 --> 00:07:35,430
The company is about to collapse.

139
00:07:35,430 --> 00:07:36,780
And you're still
being picky about the job?

140
00:07:37,430 --> 00:07:38,480
Once we turn things around,

141
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:40,880
I'll make you the Chief Financial Officer
of Wangshi Tower.

142
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:46,240
You'll be in charge of all the money.

143
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:49,830
If you go back on your word,

144
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,360
I'll kill you.

145
00:07:52,570 --> 00:07:54,310
All you ever think about
is killing people.

146
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,510
(Noble Bank)
Deposit your money and earn generous returns.

147
00:08:06,270 --> 00:08:08,430
She actually came up
with a way to give money away.

148
00:08:09,190 --> 00:08:10,800
Has that woman gone crazy?

149
00:08:13,390 --> 00:08:14,720
(For the Chief
Financial Officer position...)

150
00:08:16,460 --> 00:08:17,380
(Noble Bank. Deposit your money
and earn generous returns.)

151
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,550
I'm the greatest assassin in the world,

152
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:43,630
and here I am doing this.

153
00:08:49,940 --> 00:08:53,420
(Noble Bank)

154
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:59,840
- Great!
- Great!

155
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,320
Happy Grand Opening!

156
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,390
(To attract customers.)

157
00:09:08,670 --> 00:09:09,630
(That crazy woman)

158
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:11,630
(actually dressed me up like this.)

159
00:09:14,510 --> 00:09:15,240
Miss,

160
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:18,180
is it true that your bank really
pays generous returns on deposits?

161
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,440
Are you blind?

162
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,630
Why is she so rude?

163
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:22,710
Deposit one hundred taels.

164
00:09:22,910 --> 00:09:24,000
(Grand Opening Special)
Earn three taels a year.

165
00:09:24,190 --> 00:09:25,320
It's all in black and white.

166
00:09:25,750 --> 00:09:26,960
We'll honor it when it's due.

167
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,080
Are you blind or what?

168
00:09:33,270 --> 00:09:33,910
Stand properly.

169
00:09:35,510 --> 00:09:36,240
What's going on?

170
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,630
Come take a look!

171
00:09:39,630 --> 00:09:42,000
Grand Opening Specials at Noble Bank!

172
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,240
Deposits are completely free,

173
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:45,240
and you'll even receive real silver.

174
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,270
Deposit one hundred taels,

175
00:09:46,270 --> 00:09:48,390
and we'll return
one hundred and three taels.

176
00:09:49,510 --> 00:09:50,480
Really?

177
00:09:50,870 --> 00:09:52,600
So if I deposit one hundred taels,

178
00:09:52,910 --> 00:09:53,870
and do nothing,

179
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:54,960
a year later,

180
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,790
I'll have one hundred and three taels?

181
00:09:57,030 --> 00:09:57,910
That's right.

182
00:09:57,910 --> 00:09:59,360
And our owner

183
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:01,790
- is the Second Prince.
- That's an incredible offer!

184
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,120
We guarantee every payment.

185
00:10:03,270 --> 00:10:04,440
If we fail to honor it,

186
00:10:04,710 --> 00:10:07,030
the Court of Judicial Review
will deal with us personally.

187
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:09,000
What a great deal!

188
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:09,750
- Exactly.
- That's right.

189
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:12,200
In the past, you even had to pay
the bank to safeguard your money.

190
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:12,670
That's wonderful.

191
00:10:12,670 --> 00:10:14,120
If you kept your money at home,

192
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,870
you'd always worry about thieves.

193
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,510
Isn't this basically free money?

194
00:10:17,700 --> 00:10:18,910
I'd be a fool not to deposit it.

195
00:10:18,910 --> 00:10:20,240
I want to deposit!

196
00:10:20,270 --> 00:10:21,270
Line up!

197
00:10:21,270 --> 00:10:22,240
Form a line.

198
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,030
I want to make a deposit.

199
00:10:23,030 --> 00:10:23,670
Come on!

200
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,150
This way, please.

201
00:10:25,150 --> 00:10:26,380
I'd like to deposit three hundred taels.

202
00:10:26,390 --> 00:10:28,000
Come on! This way, please.

203
00:10:28,010 --> 00:10:28,870
I'd like to deposit five hundred taels.

204
00:10:28,870 --> 00:10:29,440
I'd like to deposit one thousand taels.

205
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,240
No cutting in line.

206
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:32,840
Wow.

207
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:34,670
Jiuzhu.

208
00:10:34,670 --> 00:10:35,790
What are you doing?

209
00:10:35,790 --> 00:10:36,900
I'd like to deposit three hundred taels.

210
00:10:38,270 --> 00:10:38,750
Come on.

211
00:10:41,790 --> 00:10:43,000
Hurry!

212
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,480
(At this rate,)

213
00:10:46,670 --> 00:10:49,480
(my little goal
will soon become a reality.)

214
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,360
Tower Master,

215
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,630
the people making deposits

216
00:10:52,630 --> 00:10:54,690
are already lining up all the way
to the end of the street.

217
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:55,840
I did the math.

218
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,630
Based on today's deposits,

219
00:10:58,030 --> 00:10:59,270
we'll be paying out

220
00:10:59,270 --> 00:11:00,840
quite a bit in interest after a year.

221
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:01,790
Can this business

222
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:03,480
really work?

223
00:11:03,910 --> 00:11:04,910
Tell me.

224
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:08,270
When ordinary people
deposit money in a bank,

225
00:11:08,770 --> 00:11:10,150
will they withdraw it the next day?

226
00:11:11,150 --> 00:11:12,030
Of course not.

227
00:11:12,630 --> 00:11:15,120
Most people are saving
to buy a house or land,

228
00:11:15,670 --> 00:11:17,750
or for their children's weddings.

229
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:20,360
Leaving it there for months
is perfectly normal.

230
00:11:20,790 --> 00:11:21,600
So while their money

231
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:24,270
is sitting in our bank,

232
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:25,870
what can we do with it?

233
00:11:30,390 --> 00:11:31,840
You mean

234
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:33,720
make money with money?

235
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:35,670
You're a quick learner.

236
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:38,630
I've often wondered, Tower Master,

237
00:11:38,630 --> 00:11:39,510
where you come up with

238
00:11:39,510 --> 00:11:41,270
so many brilliant ideas.

239
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:44,120
Could you really be
someone from beyond this world?

240
00:11:45,670 --> 00:11:47,790
(He's starting to see right through me.)

241
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:50,320
- They're here!
- Great!

242
00:11:51,030 --> 00:11:52,200
I heard

243
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:54,320
Yuanhe's confinement will be over soon.

244
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,480
I wonder how much longer our bank

245
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,720
can stay open.

246
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,840
If that pest gets out,

247
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,480
will we still have any peaceful days?

248
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:06,360
I need to find a way

249
00:12:06,670 --> 00:12:08,440
to keep him confined.

250
00:12:23,390 --> 00:12:24,440
This is for you.

251
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,400
This crossbow may be small,

252
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:27,960
but within three paces,

253
00:12:28,070 --> 00:12:29,600
it can kill a man with a single shot.

254
00:12:32,670 --> 00:12:33,120
Thank...

255
00:12:34,510 --> 00:12:36,600
Thank you for this gift, Your Highness.

256
00:12:46,300 --> 00:12:48,030
(Qingqing likes
little gadgets like these.)

257
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,440
(While I have the chance,)

258
00:12:49,450 --> 00:12:51,170
(I'll make
a few more for her protection.)

259
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:51,750
You...

260
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:53,600
How dare you show up here!

261
00:13:02,630 --> 00:13:03,200
Your Highness.

262
00:13:23,870 --> 00:13:25,670
(The Tower Master of Wangshi Tower.)

263
00:13:55,820 --> 00:13:59,180
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

264
00:13:59,940 --> 00:14:03,340
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

265
00:14:04,100 --> 00:14:05,860
♪Your smile♪

266
00:14:06,100 --> 00:14:08,380
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

267
00:14:08,380 --> 00:14:12,060
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

268
00:14:12,540 --> 00:14:15,860
♪Yet I stand before you♪

269
00:14:16,580 --> 00:14:20,420
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

270
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:22,740
♪Though fate tries♪

271
00:14:22,740 --> 00:14:25,340
♪To make us pass each other by♪

272
00:14:25,540 --> 00:14:28,980
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

273
00:14:29,220 --> 00:14:30,860
♪Though time slips by♪

274
00:14:30,860 --> 00:14:32,620
♪As day turns into night♪

275
00:14:33,140 --> 00:14:37,180
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

276
00:14:37,580 --> 00:14:39,980
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

277
00:14:39,980 --> 00:14:41,740
♪Blessed by fate♪

278
00:14:41,740 --> 00:14:46,900
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

279
00:14:46,900 --> 00:14:49,340
♪Your smiling face♪

280
